7. Fireball (Gillan, Blackmore, Glover, Lord, Paice) - 3:24
8. Demon's Eye (Gillan, Blackmore, Glover, Lord, Paice) - 5:20
9. Highway Star (Gillan, Blackmore, Glover, Lord, Paice) - 6:09
10. Smoke on the Water (Gillan, Blackmore, Glover, Lord, Paice) - 5:41
